Class Tuple.Empty<E>

java.lang.Object
civitas.celestis.util.tuple.Tuple.Empty<E>

public static final class Tuple.Empty<E> extends Object implements Tuple<E>
An empty tuple. This is only used as a placeholder instead of null values.
